 !Pasted image 20260308220030.png
 &lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="true">https://local-obsidian-sync.github.io/Obsidian-RSS/index.html?note=%D0%A2%D0%B5%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B0%20%D0%92%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B8%D0%BD%D1%8C%D0%BE%D0%BD%D0%B0</guid><pubDate>Sun, 08 Mar 2026 22:00:32 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Свойства трапеции</title><link>https://local-obsidian-sync.github.io/Obsidian-RSS/index.html?note=%D0%A1%D0%B2%D0%BE%D0%B9%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B2%D0%B0%20%D1%82%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%86%D0%B8%D0%B8</link><description>&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;!Pasted image 20260308215306.png
